2015-05-18 08:23:43		[irc]  /server  list|listfull [<server>]
2015-05-18 08:23:43		                add <server> <hostname>[/<port>] [-temp] [-<option>[=<value>]] [-no<option>]
2015-05-18 08:23:43		                copy|rename <server> <new_name>
2015-05-18 08:23:43		                reorder <server> [<server>...]
2015-05-18 08:23:43		                del|keep <server>
2015-05-18 08:23:43		                deloutq|jump|raw
2015-05-18 08:23:43		list, add or remove IRC servers
2015-05-18 08:23:43		    list: list servers (without argument, this list is displayed)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		listfull: list servers with detailed info for each server
2015-05-18 08:23:43		     add: create a new server
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  server: server name, for internal and display use
2015-05-18 08:23:43		hostname: name or IP address of server, with optional port (default: 6667), many addresses can be separated by a comma
2015-05-18 08:23:43		    temp: create temporary server (not saved)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  option: set option for server (for boolean option, value can be omitted)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		nooption: set boolean option to 'off' (for example: -nossl)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		    copy: duplicate a server
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  rename: rename a server
2015-05-18 08:23:43		 reorder: reorder list of servers
2015-05-18 08:23:43		    keep: keep server in config file (for temporary servers only)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		     del: delete a server
2015-05-18 08:23:43		 deloutq: delete messages out queue for all servers (all messages WeeChat is currently sending)
2015-05-18 08:23:43		    jump: jump to server buffer
2015-05-18 08:23:43		     raw: open buffer with raw IRC data
2015-05-18 08:23:43		Examples:
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server listfull
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server add oftc irc.oftc.net/6697 -ssl -autoconnect
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server add oftc6 irc6.oftc.net/6697 -ipv6 -ssl
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server add freenode2 chat.eu.freenode.net/6667,chat.us.freenode.net/6667
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server add freenode3 chat.freenode.net -password=mypass
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server copy oftc oftcbis
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server rename oftc newoftc
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server reorder oftc freenode
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server del freenode
2015-05-18 08:23:43		  /server deloutq
