2015-05-27 10:29:06		  server: server name, for internal and display use
2015-05-27 10:29:06		hostname: name or IP address of server, with optional port (default: 6667), many addresses can be separated by a comma
2015-05-27 10:29:06		    temp: create temporary server (not saved)
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  option: set option for server (for boolean option, value can be omitted)
2015-05-27 10:29:06		nooption: set boolean option to 'off' (for example: -nossl)
2015-05-27 10:29:06		    copy: duplicate a server
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  rename: rename a server
2015-05-27 10:29:06		 reorder: reorder list of servers
2015-05-27 10:29:06		    keep: keep server in config file (for temporary servers only)
2015-05-27 10:29:06		     del: delete a server
2015-05-27 10:29:06		 deloutq: delete messages out queue for all servers (all messages WeeChat is currently sending)
2015-05-27 10:29:06		    jump: jump to server buffer
2015-05-27 10:29:06		     raw: open buffer with raw IRC data
2015-05-27 10:29:06		Examples:
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server listfull
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server add freenode chat.freenode.net
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server add freenode chat.freenode.net/6697 -ssl -autoconnect
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server add chatspike irc.chatspike.net/6667,irc.duckspike.net/6667
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server copy freenode freenode-test
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server rename freenode-test freenode2
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server reorder freenode2 freenode
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server del freenode
2015-05-27 10:29:06		  /server deloutq
